BeanReplicator
public static interface BeanReplicator.AdapterInternal
extends BeanReplicator.Adapter

Internal extension of the BeanReplicator.Adapter interface which provides a Set of BeanReplicator.AdapterInternal.Handler instances which can be used to copy concrete source objects.

BeanReplicator.AdapterInternal instances have to be thread safe. This allows to use a single BeanReplicator.AdapterInternal instance by multiple Threads

Omnaest
